<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
		<title>{{ shop.name }}</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<style>
			body {
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				font-family: "roboto", sans-serif;
				color: {{ theme.fontColor }};
				background-color: {{ theme.backgroundColor }};
			}
			.container {
				width : 100%;
                max-width: 1200px;
                margin: 0 auto;
			}
			h1 {
				background-color: {{ theme.colorMenu }};
				color: {{ theme.fontColor }};
				font-size: 2rem;
				margin-top: 0;
				padding: 1rem;
			}
            .banner {
                width: 100%;
                height: 300px;
                background-size: cover;
                background-position: center;
                background-repeat: no-repeat;
            }
			p {
				font-size: 1.2rem;
			}
            img {
                width: 10%;
                height: auto;
            }
		</style>
		<div class="container">
            <div class="banner">
                <img src="{{ absolute_url(asset('/images/logos/' ~ logo.image)) }}" alt="{{ logo.name }}">
                <h1>Bonjour {{ user.firstname }}</h1>
            </div>
            <p>Pour red√©finir un mot de passe, merci de suivre ce lien</p>
            <a href="{{ url('reset_password', {token: resetToken.token}) }}">{{ url('reset_password', {token: resetToken.token}) }}</a>
            <p>Ce lien expirera dans {{ resetToken.expirationMessageKey|trans(resetToken.expirationMessageData, 'ResetPasswordBundle') }}.</p>
            <p>Merci</p>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
